{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2318,"text":"The brain is an amazing and complex organ."},{"time":5627,"text":"And while many people\nare fascinated by the brain,"},{"time":8093,"text":"they can't really tell you that much"},{"time":9865,"text":"about the properties\nabout how the brain works"},{"time":12142,"text":"because we don't teach\nneuroscience in schools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":14455,"text":"And one of the reasons\nwhy is that the equipment"},{"time":16898,"text":"is so complex and so expensive"},{"time":19557,"text":"that it's really only done at major\nuniversities and large institutions."},{"time":23703,"text":"And so in order to be able\nto access the brain,"},{"time":25942,"text":"you really need to dedicate your life"},{"time":27767,"text":"and spend six and a half years\nas a graduate student"},{"time":30247,"text":"just to become a neuroscientist\nto get access to these tools."}]},{"cues":[{"time":33202,"text":"And that's a shame\nbecause one out of five of us,"},{"time":35539,"text":"that's 20 percent of the entire world,\nwill have a neurological disorder."},{"time":39365,"text":"And there are zero cures\nfor these diseases."},{"time":42796,"text":"And so it seems that\nwhat we should be doing"},{"time":45015,"text":"is reaching back earlier\nin the eduction process"},{"time":47432,"text":"and teaching students about neuroscience\nso that in the future,"},{"time":52009,"text":"they may be thinking about possibly\nbecoming a brain scientist."}]},{"cues":[{"time":56064,"text":"When I was a graduate student,\nmy lab mate Tim Marzullo and myself,"},{"time":59758,"text":"decided that what if we took\nthis complex equipment that we have"},{"time":63639,"text":"for studying the brain and made it simple\nenough and affordable enough"},{"time":67038,"text":"that anyone that you know, an amateur\nor a high school student,"},{"time":70354,"text":"could learn and actually participate\nin the discovery of neuroscience."}]},{"cues":[{"time":73836,"text":"And so we did just that."},{"time":75573,"text":"A few years ago, we started\na company called Backyard Brains"},{"time":78466,"text":"and we make DIY neuroscience equipment\nand I brought some here tonight,"},{"time":82871,"text":"and I want to do some demonstrations."},{"time":85377,"text":"You guys want to see some?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":86811,"text":"So I need a volunteer."},{"time":89774,"text":"So right before -- what is your name?\n(Applause)"},{"time":92027,"text":"Sam Kelly: Sam."},{"time":93070,"text":"Greg Gage: All right, Sam, I'm going\nto record from your brain."},{"time":96095,"text":"Have you had this before?"},{"time":97849,"text":"SK: No."},{"time":98950,"text":"GG: I need you to stick out\nyour arm for science,"},{"time":101264,"text":"roll up your sleeve a bit,"},{"time":102833,"text":"So what I'm going to do,\nI'm putting electrodes on your arm,"},{"time":105713,"text":"and you're probably wondering,"},{"time":107202,"text":"I just said I'm going to record from your\nbrain, what am I doing with your arm?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":110941,"text":"Well, you have about 80 billion neurons\ninside your brain right now."},{"time":114175,"text":"They're sending electrical messages\nback and forth, and chemical messages."},{"time":117663,"text":"But some of your neurons\nright here in your motor cortex"},{"time":120336,"text":"are going to send messages down\nwhen you move your arm like this."},{"time":123431,"text":"They're going to go down\nacross your corpus callosum,"},{"time":125915,"text":"down onto your spinal cord\nto your lower motor neuron"},{"time":128449,"text":"out to your muscles here,"},{"time":129718,"text":"and that electrical discharge\nis going to be picked up"},{"time":132327,"text":"by these electrodes right here"},{"time":133861,"text":"and we're going to be able to listen"},{"time":135583,"text":"to exactly what your brain\nis going to be doing."},{"time":137835,"text":"So I'm going to turn this on for a second."}]},{"cues":[{"time":139835,"text":"Have you ever heard\nwhat your brain sounds like?"},{"time":142131,"text":"SK: No."},{"time":143166,"text":"GG: Let's try it out.\nSo go ahead and squeeze your hand."},{"time":145900,"text":"(Rumbling)"},{"time":146972,"text":"So what you're listening to,"},{"time":148848,"text":"so this is your motor units\nhappening right here."},{"time":152111,"text":"Let's take a look at it as well."},{"time":154192,"text":"So I'm going to stand over here,"},{"time":157009,"text":"and I'm going to open up our app here."},{"time":160028,"text":"So now I want you to squeeze."},{"time":161727,"text":"(Rumbling)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":162816,"text":"So right here, these are the motor units\nthat are happening"},{"time":165674,"text":"from her spinal cord\nout to her muscle right here,"},{"time":168133,"text":"and as she's doing it,"},{"time":169355,"text":"you're seeing the electrical activity\nthat's happening here."},{"time":172189,"text":"You can even click here\nand try to see one of them."},{"time":174630,"text":"So keep doing it really hard."},{"time":176101,"text":"So now we've paused"},{"time":177171,"text":"on one motor action potential that's\nhappening right now inside of your brain."}]},{"cues":[{"time":181451,"text":"Do you guys want to see some more?"},{"time":183227,"text":"(Applause)"},{"time":184810,"text":"That's interesting,\nbut let's get it better."},{"time":186954,"text":"I need one more volunteer."},{"time":189857,"text":"What is your name, sir?"},{"time":192000,"text":"Miguel Goncalves: Miguel."},{"time":193269,"text":"GG: Miguel, all right."},{"time":194400,"text":"You're going to stand right here."},{"time":195976,"text":"So when you're moving your arm like this,"},{"time":197968,"text":"your brain is sending a signal\ndown to your muscles right here."},{"time":201083,"text":"I want you to move your arm as well."},{"time":202857,"text":"So your brain is going to send\na signal down to your muscles."},{"time":205731,"text":"And so it turns out that there is\na nerve that's right here"},{"time":209580,"text":"that runs up here that innervates\nthese three fingers,"},{"time":212336,"text":"and it's close enough to the skin\nthat we might be able"},{"time":215012,"text":"to stimulate that so that what we can do"},{"time":217346,"text":"is copy your brain signals\ngoing out to your hand"},{"time":220832,"text":"and inject it into your hand,"},{"time":222353,"text":"so that your hand will move\nwhen your brain tells your hand to move."},{"time":225726,"text":"So in a sense, she will take away\nyour free will"},{"time":228933,"text":"and you will no longer have\nany control over this hand."},{"time":231964,"text":"You with me?"}]},{"cues":[{"time":233567,"text":"So I just need to hook you up."},{"time":235618,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":237369,"text":"So I'm going to find your ulnar nerve,"},{"time":239430,"text":"which is probably right around here."},{"time":242630,"text":"You don't know what you're signing up for"},{"time":244631,"text":"when you come up."},{"time":245734,"text":"So now I'm going to move away\nand we're going to plug it in"},{"time":248524,"text":"to our human-to-human interface over here."}]},{"cues":[{"time":252345,"text":"Okay, so Sam, I want you\nto squeeze your hand again."},{"time":257194,"text":"Do it again. Perfect."},{"time":259152,"text":"So now I'm going to hook you up\nover here so that you get the --"},{"time":262155,"text":"It's going to feel\na little bit weird at first,"},{"time":264399,"text":"this is going to feel like a --\n(Laughter)"},{"time":266863,"text":"You know, when you lose your free will,\nand someone else becomes your agent,"},{"time":270680,"text":"it does feel a bit strange."}]},{"cues":[{"time":272306,"text":"Now I want you to relax your hand."},{"time":274208,"text":"Sam, you're with me?"},{"time":275532,"text":"So you're going to squeeze."},{"time":276997,"text":"I'm not going to turn it on yet,\nso go ahead and give it a squeeze."}]},{"cues":[{"time":280284,"text":"So now, are you ready, Miguel?"},{"time":282240,"text":"MG: Ready as I'll ever be."},{"time":284062,"text":"GG: I've turned it on, so go ahead\nand turn your hand."},{"time":287265,"text":"Do you feel that a little bit?\nMG: Nope."},{"time":289298,"text":"GG: Okay, do it again?\nMG: A little bit."},{"time":291198,"text":"GG: A little bit? (Laughter)"},{"time":292884,"text":"So relax."},{"time":293909,"text":"So hit it again."},{"time":295325,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":296521,"text":"Oh, perfect, perfect."},{"time":298226,"text":"So relax, do it again."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300110,"text":"All right, so right now,"},{"time":302878,"text":"your brain is controlling your arm\nand it's also controlling his arm,"},{"time":307279,"text":"so go ahead and just do it one more time."},{"time":309471,"text":"All right, so it's perfect. (Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":311504,"text":"So now, what would happen\nif I took over my control of your hand?"},{"time":315265,"text":"And so, just relax your hand."},{"time":317508,"text":"What happens?"},{"time":319726,"text":"Ah, nothing."},{"time":320760,"text":"Why not?"},{"time":322298,"text":"Because the brain has to do it."},{"time":323993,"text":"So you do it again."},{"time":325346,"text":"All right, that's perfect."}]},{"cues":[{"time":327780,"text":"Thank you guys for being\nsuch a good sport."},{"time":330319,"text":"This is what's happening\nall across the world --"},{"time":332575,"text":"electrophysiology!"},{"time":333911,"text":"We're going to bring on\nthe neuro-revolution."}]},{"cues":[{"time":336158,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":337175,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}